text: Karnaukhovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Zaboryinskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 165 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km south-west from Beryozovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
title: Karnaukhovo, Zaboryinskoye Rural Settlement, Beryozovsky District, Perm Krai
